p.d: From Grammy winners to those just starting out, Soul & Jazz LIVE! features artists from around the world performing original material captured as part of a live recorded studio session. Episode 5 includes Resolution 88, Push, Camilla George, Laila Biali, A/B Trio, Nubiyan Twist, Rick Leon James, Avery.Sunshine, Tropica, and the Philip Clout Quartet. Produced by Spacerocket Media for SoulandJazz.com, this is the fifth in a six-part series featuring performances captured since late 2016.
